<title>SOUTH KOREA: Trade in Tae Sung shrs halted on rumours.</title>
<headline>Trade in Tae Sung shrs halted on rumours.</headline>
<dateline>SEOUL 1997-06-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Korea Stock Exchange on Saturday suspended trading in shares of Tae Sung Machinery and Construction Co, citing rumours that the company had defaulted on debt payments, an exchange statement said.</p>
<p>Tae Sung officials were not immediately available for comment.</p>
